MANDATORY ATTRIBUTION CONDITIONS

The following attribution conditions are NON-NEGOTIABLE and must be satisfied
at all times. Failure to comply constitutes copyright infringement and a
material breach of this License.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CONDITION 1 — PROJECT DOCUMENTATION ATTRIBUTION
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

If you use, distribute, publish, host, or deploy this software or any
portion of it — whether the project is public or private, commercial or
non-commercial, storefront-based or headless/API-only — your project's
primary documentation file (README, landing page, or equivalent) MUST
contain a clearly visible attribution section that includes ALL of the
following fields exactly as written:

    Based on Vridhira — E-Commerce for Indian Artisans
    Original author: Himanshu (https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu)
    Source: https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu/vridhira-frontend
    License: Vridhira Attribution License v2.0

All four fields are required. No field may be omitted, paraphrased,
summarised, or replaced with a vague reference such as "inspired by a
GitHub project." The attribution must:

  • Be visible without expanding collapsed sections or hidden elements.
  • Include working hyperlinks to both URLs listed above.
  • Appear in the primary documentation file — not only in a comment,
    footnote, changelog, or secondary file.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CONDITION 2 — UI CREDITS (Deployed Applications)
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

If you deploy a live application (any publicly accessible or internally
accessible website, app, hosted service, or internal tool accessible to
any end user) built on this software, the application MUST display visible
credits to the original project at ALL times. Specifically:

  (a) The VridhiraCredits component (located at
      src/modules/layout/components/vridhira-credits/) or an equivalent
      visible UI credit block MUST remain present and rendered in the
      application footer on every page of the deployed application.

  (b) The credits MUST include working links to:
        — https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu/vridhira-frontend
        — https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu

  (c) Credits must be fully LEGIBLE at all times. The following are
      explicitly prohibited and each independently constitutes a violation:
        — font-size below 10px
        — colour contrast ratio below 3:1 against background
        — display: none
        — visibility: hidden
        — opacity below 0.3
        — position: absolute or fixed with off-screen coordinates
          (e.g. left: -9999px, top: -9999px)
        — z-index placing the element behind other elements
        — any other CSS, HTML, or JavaScript technique that renders
          the credit invisible or inaccessible to a standard user

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CONDITION 3 — CREDITS ARE ADDITIVE ONLY (Non-Removal Clause)
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

You MAY add your own credits, branding, and attribution on top of the
existing attribution.

You MAY NOT:
  • Remove, replace, hide, obscure, or comment-out any existing attribution
    text, links, or copyright notices referencing Himanshu or Vridhira.
  • Rename, refactor, or restructure the VridhiraCredits component in a way
    that removes or suppresses the original attribution from the rendered UI.
  • Modify the copyright notice at the top of any source file to remove or
    alter the original author line.

You MUST treat all existing attribution as a minimum floor — you build
on top of it, never beneath it.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CONDITION 4 — COPYRIGHT NOTICE PRESERVATION (Source Files)
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

All copies or substantial portions of this software — whether modified or
unmodified — MUST retain:
  • This License file in full, unmodified, in the root of the repository.
  • The copyright notice block at the top of every source file that contains
    one (Author, GitHub, Copyright, License header comments).

You may add additional copyright notices for your own contributions above
the existing ones. You may not alter or delete the existing notices.

